Lai Mohammed, minister of information and culture, has listed 100 achievements of the Buhari administration in 2021. Addressing a press conference in Lagos on Thursday, Mohammed said despite challenges that came with 2021, the administration made “tremendous” progress in fighting insecurity and growing the economy. “What we have done here is to highlight the major achievements, hence this is by no means exhaustive,” the minister said. “That’s why we are also giving you a list of 100 achievements of the Buhari administration in 2021. Success is not measured by the number of challenges you face, but by how you tackle the challenges.” Here are achievements as presented by Mohammed; 